Depends: ${misc:Depends}, plasma-workspace, python3
Description: PlasmaCodexBar - KDE Plasma system tray applet for monitoring AI usage limits
 A native KDE Plasma 6 system tray widget that monitors your AI usage
 limits for Claude (Anthropic) and Codex (OpenAI).
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time session and weekly usage tracking
  - Cost estimation and token counting
  - Native Plasma 6 popup interface
  - Support for Claude and Codex/ChatGPT
